title: Follow 2015 District 11 girls tennis team tournaments (BRACKETS)
text:
By Josh Folck | For lehighvalleylive.com on October 16, 2015 3:05 AM View/Post Comments 
The District 11 Class AA and AA girls tennis team tournaments are set to begin on Tuesday. 
Bethlehem Catholic is the top seed in AA and Southern Lehigh holds the No. 1 seed in AAA. 
The quarterfinals will be on Tuesday at the site of the higher-seeded teams and the semifinals will follow suit on Thursday. 
The finals are scheduled for next Saturday at Northwood Racquet Club.
